Titolo: Painter Momopie

Anno: 1990

Descrizione: Painter Momopie is a 1990 maze action video game developed and published by Sigma Enterprises for the Game Boy. The player controls the witch Momopie, with the objective being to clean all the floors in a castle, and also to avoid and counter the foes that are in it. Various spells that Momopie acquires throughout the game help her in cleaning the castle faster, and/or are able to stop the enemies within it, though at the cost of MP.

Genere: Maze 

Valutazione: N/A
